===Etymology===
From {{inh|en|enm|zele}}, from {{der|en|fro|zel}}, from {{der|en|LL.|zēlus}}, from {{der|en|grc|ζῆλος||zeal, jealousy}}, from {{m|grc|ζηλόω||to emulate, to be jealous}}. Related to {{m|en|jealous}}.

